item.title: CVE-2019-19150|2024-08-05T02:09:39.374Z -- f5 -- big-ip%20apm
item.description: On versions 15.0.0-15.0.1.1, 14.1.0-14.1.2, 14.0.0-14.0.1, 13.1.0-13.1.3.1, 12.1.0-12.1.5, and 11.5.2-11.6.5.1, the BIG-IP APM system logs the client-session-id when a per-session policy is attached to the virtual server with debug logging enabled.
